  <description>
    <p>
      Survival horror set on a remote island known as Fort Oasis. The island was once run by a community of coal miners which one day suddenly disappeared,
      leaving behind the abandoned concrete jungle to waste away.
    </p>
    <p>
      Something, clearly, has gone very wrong with this place. Upon your arrival at Fort Oasis, you receive a strange radio transmission. Someone wants to be found.
      Survive in 6 chapters, against over 8 horrifying fiends with a large assortment of weapons.
    </p>
  </description>
